   <Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCR-BLOG-LIST</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">/blog</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">전체</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">동적</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">검색, 태그/카테고리 필터, 페이지네이션, 관리자 전용 삭제/새 글 버튼</Data></Cell></Row>
